OL,6,FAnother explains: "I ended up leaving
OL,7,Fmy old job. I needed to do less but my
OL,8,Fmanager wanted me to do more. The only
OL,9,Foption was to do part-time, which I
OL,10,Fcouldn't afford to do.
OL,12,F"We could be in a much better
OL,13,Ffinancial position if we didn't
OL,14,Fexperience what we had."
OL,16,FITV News asked Lily whether she had a
OL,17,Fmessage for her mum and dad.
